<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07870</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT GRANTING HAZARD PAY TO ALL PUBLIC PROSECUTORS, ASSOCIATE PROSECUTION ATTORNEYS AND PROSECUTION ATTORNEYS DURING THEIR INCUMBENCY AND APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Grants all public prosecutors, associate prosecution attorneys and prosecution attorneys hazard pay during their incumbency in the amount equivalent to twenty-five percent (25%) of their basic monthly salary per month and shall not be subject to tax.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : “Hazard Pay for all Prosecutors Act.” </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>GATCHALIAN, WES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-06-14</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON APPROPRIATIONS ON 2018-07-30</td></tr></table>